lines.text: L.A. karate... I'm impressed.
You're good.
I get better.
Alright. No retreat, no surrender!
It's that slimeball RJ!
Stick with me, guys; you'll never go hungry.
Beat it, Brucey! Go home and play with your wooden dolly!
Bruce Lee freak, just what Kingswood needs. Why me?
Hey, who peed in the pool?
Oh can't I? I think you're forgetting whose house this is!
Don't worry, RJ will provide.
Hey, ain't no shelves built to stop THIS dancin' machine.
Hey, don't worry, I'm nobody's lunch.
This is a nice dojo, I'll probably join.
(shaking Kelly violently) Yeah, right!
I'm the best!
So it is you, son, is it not?
But this time it will be different. Russian.
You moving in?

[sarcastically]
No. We just came for the weekend. We travel light.
